大卫·吉尔莫宣传有关罗杰·沃特斯涉嫌反犹太主义的纪录片https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-promotes-documentary-on-roger-waters-alleged-anti-semitism-3509913?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=david-gilmour-promotes-documentary-昂罗杰沃特斯涉嫌反犹太主义Liberty DunworthThu, 05 Oct 2023 14:12:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3509913 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·吉尔莫和罗杰·沃特斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>罗杰斯将这部纪录片描述为“一部脆弱的、毫无歉意的宣传片”。</p><p>大卫<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-promotes-documentary-on-roger-waters-alleged-anti-semitism-3509913">·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour) 宣传有关罗杰·沃特斯 (Roger Waters) 涉嫌反犹太主义的纪录片的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·吉尔莫和罗杰·沃特斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour-Roger-Waters@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-gilmour">大卫·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour)</a>继续与前平克·弗洛伊德<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">(Pink Floyd)</a>乐队成员罗杰·沃特斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roger-waters">Roger Waters)</a>长期不和，分享了一部纪录片，详细介绍了后者涉嫌反犹太主义的实例。</p><p> David Gilmour 在 X（以前的 Twitter）上转发了一篇关于名为<em>《罗杰·沃特斯的黑暗面》</em>的纪录片的帖子，该纪录片最初由制作该项目的反对反犹太主义运动出版。</p><p>罗杰斯此前曾在其<a href="https://rogerwaters.com/roger-waters-answers-the-campaign-against-antisemitism/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方网站</a>上发帖表示反对这部纪录片， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roger-waters-hits-out-at-documentary-portraying-him-as-anti-semitic-3507269">称该项目是“脆弱的、毫无歉意的宣传片”</a> 。他还声称，它“不加区别地混合了我在不同时间和不同背景下所说或所做的事情，试图将我描绘成一个反犹太主义者，没有任何事实依据。”</p><p>吉尔莫分享的视频中，沃特斯的两名前合作者回忆了他们与这位音乐家合作的经历，以及据报道他们看到沃特斯发表反犹太言论的情况。</p><p>第一个来自沃特斯的前萨克斯管演奏家诺特伯·斯塔切尔（Nortber Statchel），他告诉英国广播公司记者约翰·韦尔（John Ware），据称这位平克·弗洛伊德音乐家曾模仿一位典型的贫穷波兰妇女，以纪念他的犹太祖先。他还回忆起另一个例子，贝斯手对一家提供“犹太食品”的餐厅表示愤怒。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> “肮脏的凯克”<br /> “犹太食品”<br /> “该死的犹太人”</p><p>罗杰·沃特斯是反犹太主义者吗？</p><p>立即观看《罗杰·沃特斯的黑暗面》并自行决定。</p><p>然后在<a href="https://t.co/7F6c6M3nk1">https://t.co/7F6c6M3nk1</a>添加您的声音。 <a href="https://t.co/eh9n15DLsn">pic.twitter.com/eh9n15DLsn</a></p><p> — 反对反犹太主义运动 (@antisemitism) <a href="https://twitter.com/antisemitism/status/1707077645559619635?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 27 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>视频中出现的第二位前合作者是音乐制作人鲍勃·埃兹林 (Bob Ezrin)，他帮助制作了乐队 1979 年的专辑《The Wall》。在视频中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyd-producer-claims-roger-waters-used-anti-semitic-language-towards-bands-agent-3505336">埃尔津回忆起沃特斯谈到乐队当时的经理布莱恩·莫里森时的情景</a>，并声称他将莫里森描述为“该死的犹太人”。</p><p>在其他地方，该报告还发现了一封 2012 年的电子邮件，其中沃特斯建议在他即将推出的节目中使用犹太人的形象和诽谤。 </p><figure id="attachment_3509920" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3509920" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3509920" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour@2000x1270.jpg" alt="大卫·吉尔莫表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/David-Gilmour@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3509920" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·吉尔莫表演。图片来源：Roberto Panucci/Corbis，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>尽管吉尔莫在分享宣传视频时没有发表评论，但这位吉他手过去曾公开谈论过这些指控。</p><p>今年早些时候，他的妻子波莉·萨姆森 (Polly Samson) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-attacks-former-pink-floyd-bandmate-roger-waters-social-media-3393588">声称沃特斯“对他腐烂的核心持反犹太主义态度”，</a>并且是“普京的辩护者，撒谎、偷窃、虚伪、避税、假唱、厌女症、嫉妒症、狂妄自大”。</p><p>吉尔莫在二月份也转发了这条推文，并告诉他的追随者，他妻子的说法“显然是真实的”。</p><p>沃特斯本人发表声明回应萨姆森的言论，称他“完全反驳[他们]”，并且这些言论“具有煽动性且极不准确”。这位音乐家还表示，他正在就萨姆森的说法“听取有关他立场的建议”。</p><p>早在六月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/us-government-slams-roger-waters-berlin-performance-as-deeply-offensive-to-jewish-people-3452623">美国国务院就沃特斯一个月前在柏林的演出也批评了</a>他，称其“严重冒犯了犹太人”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3509921" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3509921" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3509921" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Roger-Waters@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2023 年 6 月 6 日，罗杰·沃特斯 (Roger Waters) 在“This is Not A Drill”巡演期间在 O2 体育馆的舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Roger-Waters@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Roger-Waters@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Roger-Waters@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Roger-Waters@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Roger-Waters@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Roger-Waters@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3509921" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 6 月 6 日，罗杰·沃特斯 (Roger Waters) 在“This is Not A Drill”巡演期间在 O2 体育馆的舞台上表演。图片来源：Jim Dyson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在这位音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/berlin-police-investigating-roger-waters-over-nazi-style-clothing-worn-at-gig-3448657">穿着一件带有类似纳粹标志的黑色风衣出现在他的演出舞台上</a>之后，发表了上述评论。当时这位音乐家为这一选择进行了辩护，声称该片段是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roger-waters-calls-berlin-gig-controversy-a-smear-aiming-to-silence-me-3448801">反对法西斯主义、不公正和偏执的声明</a>，并称对其的批评“不诚实且具有政治动机”。</p><p>在罗杰·沃特斯的其他新闻中，上个月这位词曲作者分享了平克·弗洛伊德的《Speak To Me》和《Breathe》的新独奏版本，取自他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roger-waters-shares-new-versions-of-speak-to-me-and-breathe-from-the-dark-side-of-the-moon-redux-3502728">即将重新录制的《The Dark Side Of The Moon》版本。</a></p><p>这张专辑名为“The Dark Side Of The Moon Redux”，是 Waters 对乐队 1973 年标志性专辑的完整重新演绎，该专辑于本月晚些时候发行，以庆祝其成立 50 周年。</p><p>大卫<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-promotes-documentary-on-roger-waters-alleged-anti-semitism-3509913">·吉尔莫 (David Gilmour) 宣传有关罗杰·沃特斯 (Roger Waters) 涉嫌反犹太主义的纪录片的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 《深岩银河》开发商透露 Roguelite 衍生作品《Rogue Core》 https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/deep-rock-gactic-developer-reveals-roguelite-spin-off-rogue-core-3509944?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=deep-rock-gactic-开发商透露 Roguelite 衍生品 Rogue CoreImogen Donovan Thu, 05 Oct 2023 14:01:04 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3509944 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>玩家小队对抗地球上的神秘威胁</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/deep-rock-galactic-developer-reveals-roguelite-spin-off-rogue-core-3509944">《深岩银河》开发商透露，Roguelite 衍生作品《Rogue Core》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/deep-rock-galactic"><em>《深岩银河》</em></a>的开发商今天（9 月 5 日）发布了<em>《Rogue Core》</em> ，这是这款成功的合作射击游戏的 Roguelite 版本。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/deep-rock-galactic-survivor-finds-joy-in-breaking-the-rules-of-vampire-survivors-3461649">《深岩银河：幸存者》在打破《吸血鬼幸存者》规则中找到了乐趣</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《深岩银河：Rogue Core》</em>再次成为一款以该系列宇宙为背景的第一人称射击游戏，一到四名玩家将对抗占领了 Hoxxes IV 星球上的地雷的未知威胁。查看下面的预告片： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="深岩银河：侠盗核心 - 预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kiALb0dCsiw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>作为 Roguelite 游戏，任务涉及抢救装备，然后将其添加到玩家的武器库中。然而，一旦玩家进入围绕这些地雷的格雷尤特屏障，只有在完成任务后才允许返回他们的飞船。</p><p>玩家还可以在挥舞回收者武器时使用阶段套装和主动技能来定制每次掉落的装备。</p><p>所有级别都是按程序生成的，这意味着无法知道任务会给玩家带来什么，但是回收挖掘地点将解锁更高等级的阶段套装、套装模组和回收者武器。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ghost-ship-games">Ghost Ship Games</a>联合创始人兼<em>Rogue Core</em>总监米克尔·马丁·佩德森 (Mikkel Martin Pederson) 在一份新闻稿中表示：“我们很高兴终于能够分享我们对<em>Deep Rock Galicate</em>宇宙中下一款游戏的愿景。” </p><figure id="attachment_3509959" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3509959" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3509959 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement.jpg" alt="《深岩银河：Rogue Core》来源：Ghost Ship Games" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/deep-rock-galactic-rogue-core-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3509959" class="wp-caption-text"> 《深岩银河：Rogue Core》来源：Ghost Ship Games</figcaption></figure><p> “我们有意不将这款游戏定位为续作，因为我们仍然致力于支持<em>《深岩银河》</em>作为一款现场游戏，但我们热衷于为粉丝们提供只有衍生游戏才能提供的游戏玩法的全新体验。</p><p> “更重要的是，我们迫不及待地想开始从粉丝那里获得反馈来构建他们想玩的游戏，因为我们的开放开发过程帮助<em>《深岩银河》</em>成为了现在的游戏，”他总结道。</p><p>目前，该游戏正处于“最早期的开发阶段”，尚不清楚何时可以玩。不过，我们鼓励粉丝们在 Discord 和 Steam 上关注游戏的旅程，并且将及时邀请您进行封闭式 alpha 测试。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，一些加入工会的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dragon-age-dreadwolf"><em>《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》</em></a>开发商于 9 月份被解雇， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unionised-dragon-age-dreadwolf-developers-were-laid-off-this-week-3509741">目前正在寻求足够的遣散费</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/deep-rock-galactic-developer-reveals-roguelite-spin-off-rogue-core-3509944">《深岩银河》开发商透露，Roguelite 衍生作品《Rogue Core》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
