0x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dragon-age-dreadwolf-qa-testers-let-go-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dragon-age-dreadwolf-qa-testers-let-go-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dragon-age-dreadwolf-qa-testers-let-go-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bioware">BioWare</a>选择不再继续与<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dragon-age-dreadwolf">《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》</a>的工会开发商签订合同，</em>导致这家加拿大公司失去 13 名质量保证测试人员。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dragon-age-writer-mary-kirby-is-one-of-50-bioware-developers-that-have-been-laid-off-3487871">《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》的发行日期、预告片和最新消息</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.polygon.com/23903782/dragon-age-dreadwolf-qa-workers-laid-off-keywords-studios" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Polygon</em></a>报道，这些测试人员收到消息称，他们不会重返游戏，并于 9 月 27 日被解雇。“我们可以确认，遗憾的是，13 名埃德蒙顿员工在固定期限客户结束后现已离开公司合同，”Keywords Studios 的全球营销主管 Liz Corless 在一封电子邮件中说道。</p><p>然而，开发支持测试员 James Russwurm 告诉<em>Polygon</em> ，“最低”遣散费显然尚未支付给受影响的员工，因此 KWS Edmonton United 已向 keywords Studios 提交了就业标准投诉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3487894" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3487894" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3487894" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bioware-fires-mary-kirby-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bioware-fires-mary-kirby-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bioware-fires-mary-kirby-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bioware-fires-mary-kirby-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bioware-fires-mary-kirby-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bioware-fires-mary-kirby-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/bioware-fires-mary-kirby-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3487894" class="wp-caption-text"> 《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》图片来源：Electronic Arts</figcaption></figure><p>为BioWare提供员工的Keywords Studios Edmonton在管理层向员工施压要求其返回办公室后，于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dragon-age-dreadwolf-studios-qa-team-unanimously-vote-to-unionise-3241469">去年6月成立了工会</a>。组织允许其反对就职要求，并且在未与工会协商的情况下不允许改变其角色。</p><p> “我们鼓励所有工人争取不被剥削的权利。我希望我们能在视频游戏行业看到更多的工会，这样它就可以变得更加正常化。正如人们所说，水涨船高。”KWS 埃德蒙顿联队的一名成员在取得成功后<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/its-the-year-of-worker-power-why-unionisation-in-gaming-is-here-to-stay-3278113" target="_blank" rel="noopener">接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>说道。</p><p>由于 13 名受影响员工失去职位，工会希望获得更高的遣散费。此外，据说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dragon-age-writer-mary-kirby-is-one-of-50-bioware-developers-that-have-been-laid-off-3487871">在 2023 年 8 月裁员 50 人之后，</a> Keywords Studios 的员工正在与 BioWare 进行“讨价还价”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/diablo-4"><em>《暗黑破坏神 4</em></a> 》的“血色季节”见证了一支贪婪的吸血鬼大军入侵庇护所，玩家可以使用<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/diablo-4-season-of-blood-will-be-the-biggest-update-since-launch-3509195">新的吸血鬼力量</a>来对抗敌人。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unionised-dragon-age-dreadwolf-developers-were-laid-off-this-week-3509741">工会化后的《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》开发者本周被解雇，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
娱乐界回应 Rishi Sunak 和保守党政府的跨性别评论和政策https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-responds-to-rishi-sunak-and-tory-governments-trans-comments-and-policies-3509882?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=entertainment-世界回应圣人苏纳克和保守党政府的反式评论和政策Liberty DunworthThu, 05 Oct 2023 11:57:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsPoliticsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3509882 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在 2023 年 10 月 4 日保守党会议最后一天发表讲话。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>此前有消息称跨性别者可能被禁止进入单一性别医院</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-responds-to-rishi-sunak-and-tory-governments-trans-comments-and-policies-3509882">娱乐界对 Rishi Sunak 和保守党政府的跨性别言论和政策做出回应的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在 2023 年 10 月 4 日保守党会议最后一天发表讲话。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>娱乐界人士纷纷站出来分享他们对保守党政府试图限制跨性别群体权利的最新想法的看法。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/opinion/liz-trusss-toploader-tory-leadership-contest-3275678">Liz Truss 对 Toploader 的热爱表明我们很快就会在废话中跳舞</a></strong></li></ul><p>英国首相苏纳克在保守党会议上发表讲话时发表了上述言论，他在会上分享了他对暴力犯罪分子入狱的看法以及对跨性别群体的态度。</p><p>他首先表示，他希望确保对“虐待狂”杀手判处更严厉的监禁，并且他对此主题的看法不应被视为“有争议”的观点。</p><p> “我很清楚，有些罪行是如此令人发指，以至于那些犯下这些罪行的人应该在监狱里度过余生。因此我可以确认，我们将立法对性谋杀和虐待谋杀案判处终身监禁，不得释放。”他说。 “我们将改变这个国家，这意味着生命就是生命。现在这不应该成为一个有争议的立场，绝大多数勤奋的人都同意这一点。”</p><p>后来他将这一点与他对跨性别群体的看法联系起来，称他相信人们不能“成为他们想成为的任何性别”。他补充说：“对于父母来说，了解孩子在学校里被教授的关于人际关系的内容，对于病人来说，了解医院何时谈论男性或女性，这也不应该引起争议。”</p><p> “我们不应该被迫相信人们可以成为他们想成为的任何性别。男人就是男人，女人就是女人，这是常识。” </p><figure id="attachment_3509890" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3509890" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3509890" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak-Conference@2000x1270.jpg" alt="首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在 2023 年 10 月 4 日保守党会议最后一天发表讲话" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak-Conference@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak-Conference@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak-Conference@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak-Conference@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak-Conference@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Rishi-Sunak-Conference@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3509890" class="wp-caption-text">首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在 2023 年 10 月 4 日保守党会议最后一天发表讲话。图片来源：Ian Forsyth/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>英国政府最近提出了一项提议，该提议将阻止跨性别者进入单一性别医院。</p><p>现在，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-smith">萨姆·史密斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-bragg">比利·布拉格</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/self-esteem">自尊在内</a>的众多娱乐界成员都站出来分享了他们对这个问题的看法。</p><p> “致目前在英国的所有跨性别/非二元和性别不合格的人，”前者在 Instagram 故事中写道。 “你并不孤单。你的人性和你的生活很重要。向你们每一个人致以深深的爱x。”</p><p>布拉格同意这一观点，并引用了保守党议员李·安德森 (Lee Anderson) 之前的评论：“鉴于保守党会议上的纲领所说的内容，当李·安德森说保守党将在下一次选举中就文化进行斗争时，听起来他并不是在开玩笑。战争和打击跨性别者#TransRightsAreHumanRights。”</p><p>自尊组织的丽贝卡·露西·泰勒也发表了类似的声明，她写道：“跨性别者的生命很重要，没有人抱怨女病房里的跨性别姐妹，教育你的家人在这个可怕的时代批判性思维的重要性。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">鉴于保守党会议上的平台所说的内容，当李·安德森说保守党将在下一次选举中进行文化战争和打击跨性别者时，听起来他并不是在开玩笑<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TransRightsAreHumanRights?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#TransRightsAreHumanRights</a> <a href="https://t.co/NpgzdeQ5h4">pic.twitter.com/NpgzdeQ5h4</a></p><p> — 比利·布拉格 (@billybragg) <a href="https://twitter.com/billybragg/status/1709608289741279281?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 4 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> just a quick pop on here to retweet cabaret compliments and while I&#39;m here: trans lives matter, nobody is complaining about our trans sisters on female wards, educate your family members about the importance of critical thinking in these horrific, terrifying times.</p><p> — Rebecca Lucy Taylor (@SELFESTEEM___) <a href="https://twitter.com/SELFESTEEM___/status/1709904156419379562?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 5, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Shirley Manson of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> took to the band&#39;s Instagram stories to criticise the comments. “Please please please educate yourself about trans peoples who have existed since time began and stop punishing them,” she wrote. “Help protect them and honour them. Please do the study or shut your mouths.”</p><p> Comedian Josie Long also took to X/Twitter to share support for the trans community in light of the controversial comments. “I love my trans friends and family, and that if you&#39;re trans i love and support you! Fuck this government and their supporters into the sun,” she wrote, while model and activist Munroe Bergdorf added: “I&#39;m frustrated, angry and sad at the state of this country.”</p><p> Find more responses from the world of entertainment below.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Feels important just to say that today and every day i love my trans friends and family, and that if you&#39;re trans i love and support you! Fuck this government and their supporters into the sun.</p><p> — Josie Long manifesting the baby sleeping through (@JosieLong) <a href="https://twitter.com/JosieLong/status/1709695500264329487?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 4, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cx8uhKTL4Mq/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="displ